version_description:
We sprinkled some pixie dust on the app to bring you some fixes, including:

- assorted text and Icon size and color changes throughout the app
- we resolved a bug that causes certain sound effects to play, even when turned off in app settings
- added a notification to the trade details screen when a new comment has been added

and more!

Oo-de-lally, oo-de-lally, golly what an update!

In this version we've made it easier than ever to follow other collectors and also track who is following you.

We've also simplified our sign in process and made additional UI and stability fixes to improve the overall app experience.

Thanks for collecting with us!

Our team has been working on lots of behind the scenes magic, bug fixes and improvements. In this update:

- Missions that are ready to be claimed will now jump to the top of your Missions list!
- We corrected which cards display in the recently collected section

Update today to see these changes and more!
